<paragraph blockId="2.[151,539,690,718]" box="[151,539,690,718]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,539,690,718]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,539,690,718]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">
Genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Navas 1916" authorityName="Navas" authorityYear="1916" box="[238,539,690,718]" class="Insecta" family="Calamoceratidae" genus="Banyallarga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[238,388,691,718]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">Banyallarga</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Navas, L." box="[396,539,690,717]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" pagination="71 - 80" refId="ref6357" refString="Navas, L. (1916) Neuroptera nova Americana. Memorie della Pontificia Accademia Romana dei Nuovi Lincei, (2) 2, 71 - 80." type="journal article" year="1916">Navás 1916</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="580" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,763,862]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">
Endemic to the Neotropics, this genus is represented by 17 species distributed from 
<collectingCountry box="[1105,1220,763,789]" name="Nicaragua" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">Nicaragua</collectingCountry>
south to 
<collectingCountry box="[1325,1436,763,789]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Prather, A. L." box="[158,307,799,825]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" pagination="1 - 76" refId="ref6469" refString="Prather, A. L. (2004) Revision of the Neotropical caddisfly genus Banyallarga (Trichoptera: Calamoceratidae). Zootaxa, 435 (1), 1 - 76. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 435.1.1" type="journal article" year="2004">Prather 2004</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Holzenthal, R. W. &amp; Calor, A. R." box="[316,600,799,825]" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" pagination="1 - 566" refId="ref5887" refString="Holzenthal, R. W. &amp; Calor, A. R. (2017) Catalog of the Neotropical Trichoptera (Caddisflies). Zookeys, 654, 1 - 566. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 654.9516" type="journal article" year="2017">Holzenthal &amp; Calor 2017</bibRefCitation>
). Previously, a single species, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Resh 1983)" baseAuthorityName="Resh" baseAuthorityYear="1983" box="[930,1298,799,825]" class="Insecta" family="Calamoceratidae" genus="Banyallarga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="580" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fortuna">
<emphasis box="[930,1156,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">Banyallarga fortuna</emphasis>
(Resh 1983)
</taxonomicName>
(in 
<bibRefCitation author="Denning, D. G. &amp; Resh, V. H. &amp; Hogue, C. L." pageId="2" pageNumber="580" pagination="181 - 191" refId="ref5401" refString="Denning, D. G., Resh, V. H. &amp; Hogue, C. L. (1983) New species of Phylloicus and a new Neotropical genus of Calamoceratidae (Trichoptera). Aquatic Insects, 5 (3), 181 - 191. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 01650428309361143" type="journal article" year="1983">
Denning 
<emphasis box="[151,200,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">et al</emphasis>
. 1983
</bibRefCitation>
), was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[520,612,836,862]" name="Panama" pageId="2" pageNumber="580">Panama</collectingCountry>
. We here add a second species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
